cat << EOF
The Claw3 is a file browser designed as a lightweight
and portable alternative to Konqueror, Nautilus, 
Rox, and Endeavour. It features dual-pane icon views,
mime-type editing, GTK theming, filtering of 
file contents, and audio/image previews.
